### Register
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

### Login
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/Token
Content-Type: application/json

### Movies - GET ALL (JWT gerekli)
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/Movies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json


### Movies - GET BY ID (JWT gerekli)
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/Movies/{{movieId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json


### Movies - CREATE (JWT gerekli)
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/Movies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Movies - UPDATE (JWT gerekli)
